  <summary date="2021-02-10T15:19:19Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Strengthening Families for Success Act of 2020 This bill reauthorizes, establishes, and revises programs related to healthy families, parenting time arrangements, and child support. This includes temporarily waiving certain state requirements under the Temporary Assistance for Needy Families program related to the enforcement of child support orders.</summary>
